title: Hackintosh OSX Collection Pack 2006-2014
description:
Hackintosh OSX Collection Pack 2006-2014 


Collection of fine Hackintosh Tools collected from 2006 till 2014. 

This is NOT a bootable .ISO, but just a collection of files, to help you get you're own hackintosh running.

The .ISO file is hybrid, that means that there is one part with Microsoft Windows files. This will only be mounted with-in Windows Operating Systems.

And there is an other part of this .ISO that will be only mounted at Mac OS X Operating Systems.

Have fun!
